477
00:34:14,550 --> 00:34:15,856
untuk kepulangan You Yan,

478
00:34:15,880 --> 00:34:17,120
jadi mereka enggan mematuhi Tingyan.

479
00:34:17,880 --> 00:34:21,090
Walaupun hanya tinggal segumpal
jiwa, cacing kotor itu

480
00:34:21,760 --> 00:34:23,260
